{"word":"G731 - ἄῤῥητος - árrhētos - ar'-hray-tos - Unspeakable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄῤῥητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">árrhētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ar'-hray-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unspeakable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பேசப்படாதது - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unsaid, unspoken, unspeakable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and the same as <a href=\"#/G4490 - ῥητῶς - rhētōs - hray-toce'/4490\">G4490</a>; <i>unsaid</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>inexpressible:</i> - unspeakable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}